# Root build context for the Hub Cloud Build (cleanslate0 hub_rebase — context
# widened from hub/ to the repo root for npm-workspace resolution). gcloud builds
# submit reads .gcloudignore if present (else .gitignore). Keep the upload lean:
# deps install in-container (npm ci from the root lockfile), dist builds
# in-container. hub/build-info.json (the transient deploy-truth stamp) is NOT
# excluded here — it must upload for hub/Dockerfile's `COPY hub ./hub`.
**/node_modules
.git
**/dist
**/*.tgz
**/*.log
**/.DS_Store
coverage
.claude
